# Additional key metrics
getmode <- function(v) {
  uniqv <- unique(v)
  uniqv[which.max(tabulate(match(v, uniqv)))]
}
getmode(noAttritionRd$Education) # 3 (bachelors)
## [1] 3
getmode(noAttritionRd$MaritalStatus) # the majority are married
## [1] Married
